videos.description: The No. 1 Crimson Tide rocked the No. 13 Tigers, 30-12, in Tuscaloosa. Alabama, which hasn't allowed a touchdown in more than five weeks, is only one win from securing the top seed in the College Football Playoff.

videos.headline: Alabama dominates Auburn, sets sights on SEC title
